__SqlaTable__.sql:
SELECT LOAD_DATE AS LOAD_DATE
	,STATUS
	,count(1) AS total_no_of_files
	,sum(row_count) AS total_no_of_records
	,sum(file_size) AS total_file_size
FROM snowpipe__copy_history
WHERE LOAD_DATE IN (
		CURRENT_DATE () + 1
		,CURRENT_DATE ()
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 1
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 2
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 3
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 4
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 5
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 6
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 7
		)
GROUP BY LOAD_DATE
	,STATUS
ORDER BY LOAD_DATE DESC

SELECT FILE_NAME
	,STATUS
	,LAST_LOAD_TIME
	,ROW_COUNT
	,FILE_SIZE
FROM snowpipe__copy_history
WHERE LOAD_DATE IN (
		CURRENT_DATE () + 1
		,CURRENT_DATE ()
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 1
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 2
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 3
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 4
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 5
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 6
		,CURRENT_DATE () - 7
		)
	AND STATUS <> 'Loaded'
ORDER BY LOAD_DATE
	,FILE_NAME DESC;
